snippet.textDisplay: Sunidhi is far ahead of Shreya who has an extremely melodious voice but so do many other female singers who are simply not as luck as her.. Listen to Nihira, Bela Shinde, Anwesha,all sound like Shreya who herself sounds like Anuradha Paudwal/Sadhna Sargam.. Sunidhi has a more original voice in my opinion as she can sing both soft numbers as well as item songs..
